      • downloadFile

        public RxStorageBinding.RxProgressAwareSingleOperation<StorageDownloadFileResult> downloadFile(java.lang.String key,
                                                                                               java.io.File local,
                                                                                               StorageDownloadFileOptions options)
        Description copied from interface: RxStorageCategoryBehavior
        Download a file.
        Specified by:
        downloadFile in interface RxStorageCategoryBehavior
        Parameters:
        key - Remote key of file
        local - Local file to which to save
        options - Additional download options
        Returns:
        An instance of RxStorageBinding.RxStorageDownloadOperation which emits a download result or failure as a Single. It also provides progress information when the caller subscribes to RxStorageBinding.RxStorageDownloadOperation#observeProgress(). The download does not begin until subscription. You can cancel the download by disposing the single subscription.
